List Of API's


POST REQUESTS:


1. /addtocart
2. /addtowishlist
3. /removefromcart
4. /removefromwishlist
5. /additem
6. /newcollection
7. /newcategory
8. /createorder
9. /signin
10. /signup


GET REQUESTS:

1. /collections
2. /getusers/seller
3. /getusers/buyer
4. /getuser/seller/:userid
5. /getuser/buyer/:userid
6. /getitems
7. /getitems/range/:offset/:quantity
8. /getitems/city/:city
9. /getitems/city/:city/:offset/:quantity
10. /getitems/:city/:categoryid/:lookupid/:occasionid/:brand/:offset/:quantity
11. /numrecords/:city/:categoryid/:lookupid/:occasionid/:brand
12. /getitems/category/:category_id
13. /getcart/:userid
14. /getwishlist/:userid
15. /getitem/:itemcode
16. /related/:itemid


